Class OnlineKMeans<T extends DoubleVector>

java.lang.Object
  edu.ucla.sspace.clustering.OnlineKMeans<T>
All Implemented Interfaces:
Generator<OnlineClustering<T>>
public class OnlineKMeans<T extends DoubleVector>
extends Object
implements Generator<OnlineClustering<T>>

A Generator class for generating a new OnlineKMeansClustering instance. This class supports the following properties:

Property:
Default:
This variable sets the weight given to the mean vector in a rolling average of vectors.

Property:
Default: 0.35
This variable sets the threshold for merging two clusters.

Property:
Default: 15
This variable sets the maximum number of clusters used.

Author:
Keith Stevens
